S = \sum_{j=1}^k \sum_{i=j}^k a_i p^{i-j} = \sum_{i=1}^k \sum_{j=1}^i a_i p^{i-j} =  \sum_{i=1}^k a_i \dfrac{p^{i}-1}{p-1} = (p-1)^{-1} \left( n - \sum_{i=0}^k a_i \right) 
